title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\ExportFeatureValuesRequest\SnapshotExport
name: SnapshotExport
description:
Describes exporting the latest Feature values of all entities of the EntityType between [start_time, snapshot_time].

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.ExportFeatureValuesRequest.SnapshotExport

params.description: Exports Feature values as of this timestamp. If not set, retrieve values as of now. Timestamp, if present, must not have higher than millisecond precision.
